22static inline isc_result_t
23fromtext_in_apl(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
24 isc_token_t token;
25 unsigned char addr[16];
26 unsigned long afi;
27 uint8_t prefix;
28 uint8_t len;
29 bool neg;
30 char *cp, *ap, *slash;
31 int n;
32
33 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
34 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
35
36 UNUSED(type);
37 UNUSED(rdclass);
38 UNUSED(origin);
39 UNUSED(options);
40 UNUSED(callbacks);
41
42 do {
43 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
44 isc_tokentype_string, true));
45 if (token.type != isc_tokentype_string)
46 break;
47
48 cp = DNS_AS_STR(token);
49 neg = (*cp == '!');
50 if (neg)
51 cp++;
52 afi = strtoul(cp, &ap, 10);
53 if (*ap++ != ':' || cp == ap)
54 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
55 if (afi > 0xffffU)
56 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
57 slash = strchr(ap, '/');
58 if (slash == NULL || slash == ap)
59 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
60 RETTOK(isc_parse_uint8(&prefix, slash + 1, 10));
61 switch (afi) {
62 case 1:
63 *slash = '\0';
64 n = inet_pton(AF_INET, ap, addr);
65 *slash = '/';
66 if (n != 1)
67 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADDOTTEDQUAD);
68 if (prefix > 32)
69 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
70 for (len = 4; len > 0; len--)
71 if (addr[len - 1] != 0)
72 break;
73 break;
74
75 case 2:
76 *slash = '\0';
77 n = inet_pton(AF_INET6, ap, addr);
78 *slash = '/';
79 if (n != 1)
80 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADAAAA);
81 if (prefix > 128)
82 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
83 for (len = 16; len > 0; len--)
84 if (addr[len - 1] != 0)
85 break;
86 break;
87
88 default:
89 RETTOK(ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
90 }
91 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(afi, target));
92 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(prefix, target));
93 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(len | ((neg) ? 0x80 : 0), target));
94 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, addr, len));
95 } while (1);
96
97 /*
98 * Let upper layer handle eol/eof.
99 */
100 isc_lex_ungettoken(lexer, &token);
101
102 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
103}

105static inline isc_result_t
106totext_in_apl(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
107 isc_region_t sr;
108 isc_region_t ir;
109 uint16_t afi;
110 uint8_t prefix;
111 uint8_t len;
112 bool neg;
113 unsigned char buf[16];
114 char txt[sizeof(" !64000:")];
115 const char *sep = "";
116 int n;
117
118 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
119 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
120
121 UNUSED(tctx);
122
123 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
124 ir.base = buf;
125 ir.length = sizeof(buf);
126
127 while (sr.length > 0) {
128 INSIST(sr.length >= 4);
129 afi = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
130 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
131 prefix = *sr.base;
132 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
133 len = (*sr.base & 0x7f);
134 neg = (*sr.base & 0x80);
135 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
136 INSIST(len <= sr.length);
137 n = snprintf(txt, sizeof(txt), "%s%s%u:", sep,
138 neg ? "!" : "", afi);
139 INSIST(n < (int)sizeof(txt));
140 RETERR(str_totext(txt, target));
141 switch (afi) {
142 case 1:
143 INSIST(len <= 4);
144 INSIST(prefix <= 32);
145 memset(buf, 0, sizeof(buf));
146 memmove(buf, sr.base, len);
147 RETERR(inet_totext(AF_INET, &ir, target));
148 break;
149
150 case 2:
151 INSIST(len <= 16);
152 INSIST(prefix <= 128);
153 memset(buf, 0, sizeof(buf));
154 memmove(buf, sr.base, len);
155 RETERR(inet_totext(AF_INET6, &ir, target));
156 break;
157
158 default:
159 return (ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED);
160 }
161 n = snprintf(txt, sizeof(txt), "/%u", prefix);
162 INSIST(n < (int)sizeof(txt));
163 RETERR(str_totext(txt, target));
164 isc_region_consume(&sr, len);
165 sep = " ";
166 }
167 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
168}

170static inline isc_result_t
171fromwire_in_apl(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
172 isc_region_t sr, sr2;
173 isc_region_t tr;
174 uint16_t afi;
175 uint8_t prefix;
176 uint8_t len;
177
178 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
179 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
180
181 UNUSED(type);
182 UNUSED(dctx);
183 UNUSED(rdclass);
184 UNUSED(options);
185
186 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
187 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tr);
188 if (sr.length > tr.length)
189 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
190 sr2 = sr;
191
192 /* Zero or more items */
193 while (sr.length > 0) {
194 if (sr.length < 4)
195 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
196 afi = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
197 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
198 prefix = *sr.base;
199 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
200 len = (*sr.base & 0x7f);
201 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
202 if (len > sr.length)
203 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
204 switch (afi) {
205 case 1:
206 if (prefix > 32 || len > 4)
207 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
208 break;
209 case 2:
210 if (prefix > 128 || len > 16)
211 return (ISC_R_RANGE);
212 }
213 if (len > 0 && sr.base[len - 1] == 0)
214 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
215 isc_region_consume(&sr, len);
216 }
217 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr2.length);
218 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr2.base, sr2.length));
219}

221static inline isc_result_t
222towire_in_apl(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
223 UNUSED(cctx);
224
225 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
226 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
227
228 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
229}

231static inline int
232compare_in_apl(ARGS_COMPARE) {
233 isc_region_t r1;
234 isc_region_t r2;
235
236 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
237 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
238 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
239 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
240
241 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
242 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
243 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
244}
245
246static inline isc_result_t
247fromstruct_in_apl(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
248 dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl = source;
249 isc_buffer_t b;
250
251 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
252 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
253 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
254 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdtype == type);
255 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdclass == rdclass);
256 REQUIRE(apl->apl != NULL || apl->apl_len == 0);
257
258 isc_buffer_init(&b, apl->apl, apl->apl_len);
259 isc_buffer_add(&b, apl->apl_len);
260 isc_buffer_setactive(&b, apl->apl_len);
261 return(fromwire_in_apl(rdclass, type, &b, NULL, false, target));
262}
263
264static inline isc_result_t
265tostruct_in_apl(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
266 dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl = target;
267 isc_region_t r;
268
269 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
270 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
271
272 apl->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
273 apl->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
274 ISC_LINK_INIT(&apl->common, link);
275
276 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
277 apl->apl_len = r.length;
278 apl->apl = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, r.length);
279 if (apl->apl == NULL)
280 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
281
282 apl->offset = 0;
283 apl->mctx = mctx;
284 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
285}
286
287static inline void
288freestruct_in_apl(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
289 dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl = source;
290
291 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
292 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_apl);
293 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
294
295 if (apl->mctx == NULL)
296 return;
297 if (apl->apl != NULL)
298 isc_mem_free(apl->mctx, apl->apl);
299 apl->mctx = NULL;
300}

302isc_result_t
303dns_rdata_apl_first(dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl) {
304 uint32_t length;
305
306 REQUIRE(apl != NULL);
307 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_apl);
308 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
309 REQUIRE(apl->apl != NULL || apl->apl_len == 0);
310
311 /*
312 * If no APL return ISC_R_NOMORE.
313 */
314 if (apl->apl == NULL)
315 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
316
317 /*
318 * Sanity check data.
319 */
320 INSIST(apl->apl_len > 3U);
321 length = apl->apl[apl->offset + 3] & 0x7f;
322 INSIST(4 + length <= apl->apl_len);
323
324 apl->offset = 0;
325 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
326}
327
328isc_result_t
329dns_rdata_apl_next(dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl) {
330 uint32_t length;
331
332 REQUIRE(apl != NULL);
333 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_apl);
334 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
335 REQUIRE(apl->apl != NULL || apl->apl_len == 0);
336
337 /*
338 * No APL or have already reached the end return ISC_R_NOMORE.
339 */
340 if (apl->apl == NULL || apl->offset == apl->apl_len)
341 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
342
343 /*
344 * Sanity check data.
345 */
346 INSIST(apl->offset < apl->apl_len);
347 INSIST(apl->apl_len > 3U);
348 INSIST(apl->offset <= apl->apl_len - 4U);
349 length = apl->apl[apl->offset + 3] & 0x7f;
350 /*
351 * 16 to 32 bits promotion as 'length' is 32 bits so there is
352 * no overflow problems.
353 */
354 INSIST(4 + length + apl->offset <= apl->apl_len);
355
356 apl->offset += 4 + length;
357 return ((apl->offset < apl->apl_len) ? ISC_R_SUCCESS : ISC_R_NOMORE);
358}
359
360isc_result_t
361dns_rdata_apl_current(dns_rdata_in_apl_t *apl, dns_rdata_apl_ent_t *ent) {
362 uint32_t length;
363
364 REQUIRE(apl != NULL);
365 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_apl);
366 REQUIRE(apl->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
367 REQUIRE(ent != NULL);
368 REQUIRE(apl->apl != NULL || apl->apl_len == 0);
369 REQUIRE(apl->offset <= apl->apl_len);
370
371 if (apl->offset == apl->apl_len)
372 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
373
374 /*
375 * Sanity check data.
376 */
377 INSIST(apl->apl_len > 3U);
378 INSIST(apl->offset <= apl->apl_len - 4U);
379 length = (apl->apl[apl->offset + 3] & 0x7f);
380 /*
381 * 16 to 32 bits promotion as 'length' is 32 bits so there is
382 * no overflow problems.
383 */
384 INSIST(4 + length + apl->offset <= apl->apl_len);
385
386 ent->family = (apl->apl[apl->offset] << 8) + apl->apl[apl->offset + 1];
387 ent->prefix = apl->apl[apl->offset + 2];
388 ent->length = length;
389 ent->negative = (apl->apl[apl->offset + 3] & 0x80);
390 if (ent->length != 0)
391 ent->data = &apl->apl[apl->offset + 4];
392 else
393 ent->data = NULL;
394 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
395}

399 return (apl->apl_len);

413static inline isc_result_t
414digest_in_apl(ARGS_DIGEST) {
415 isc_region_t r;
416
417 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_apl);
418 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
419
420 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
421
422 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
423}
